(524, 'Summon Monster VIII', 'Conjuration', 'see text for summon monster I', 'V, S, F/DF', '1 round', 'Close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)', '', '1 round/level (D)', 'None', 'No', 'This spell functions like summon monster I,  except that you can summon one creature from the 8th-level list, 1d3 creatures of the same kind from the 7th-level list, or 1d4+1 creatures of the same kind from a lower-level list.'),
